Wijnaldum: &quot;We started well - we put away our chances, we made few mistakes and they had few chances. We have a clean sheet again. It's good.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wijnaldum: &quot;If you don't run for yourself you run for others. We did everything right tonight.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;We have learnt from our mistakes against Sevilla, we have learnt from our mistakes against Spurs - we will be ready.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;This is one of the better experiences as manager of this club! There will be difficult moments for sure, but for tonight, it was nice!&quot;

Klopp: &quot;If we perform like we did tonight, as clinical as we were tonight, it is obviously a threat, 100%.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;I am sure somebody will make a story tomorrow about Jordan Henderson not starting, but I have to make hard decisions. He will start the next game 100%.&quot;
